---
<Base
  title="EM Music Produções - Prod. Eder Machado"
  description="Grave, masterize, aprenda produção musical ou pegue loops prontos. Fale direto com o Eder Machado."
  redeAtual="EM Music Produções"
>
  <SiteNav slot="nav" whatsappUrl={WHATSAPP_URL} />
  <SideTabs siteLabel="EM Music Produções" />

  <main>
    <!-- HERO estilo Kronoxx: fundo em movimento (video real quando existir, ou onda
         animada leve como base/fallback), tipografia gigante em cima -->
    <section id="topo" class="relative flex min-h-[100svh] flex-col items-center justify-center overflow-hidden px-6 py-24">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 overflow-hidden" aria-hidden="true">
        {hasHeroVideo ? (
          <video
            class="h-full w-full object-cover opacity-60"
            autoplay
            muted
            loop
            playsinline
            preload="none"
          >
            <source src="/videos/hero-bg.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
          </video>
        ) : (
          <div class="hero-yt-wrap">
            <iframe
              class="hero-yt-iframe"
              src={heroYoutubeEmbed}
              title=""
              frameborder="0"
              allow="autoplay; encrypted-media"
              tabindex="-1"
            ></iframe>
          </div>
        )}
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-black/80 via-black/15 to-black"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-3xl text-center [text-shadow:0_1px_3px_rgba(0,0,0,0.85),0_2px_10px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)]">
        <img
          src="/images/em-music-logo.png"
          alt="EM Music Produções"
          class="mx-auto h-12 w-auto sm:h-14"
          width="1400"
          height="586"
        />
        <div class="mx-auto mt-5 flex h-9 items-end justify-center gap-1" aria-hidden="true">
          <span class="eq-bar w-1.5 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-t from-brand-purple to-brand-pink"></span>
          <span class="eq-bar w-1.5 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-t from-brand-purple to-brand-pink"></span>
          <span class="eq-bar w-1.5 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-t from-brand-purple to-brand-pink"></span>
          <span class="eq-bar w-1.5 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-t from-brand-purple to-brand-pink"></span>
          <span class="eq-bar w-1.5 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-t from-brand-purple to-brand-pink"></span>
          <span class="eq-bar w-1.5 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-t from-brand-purple to-brand-pink"></span>
          <span class="eq-bar w-1.5 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-t from-brand-purple to-brand-pink"></span>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-6 font-display text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-brand-pink sm:text-sm">
          Chegou pelo adesivo do carro?
        </p>
        <h1 class="balance mt-5 font-hero text-6xl leading-[1.15] text-white sm:text-7xl sm:leading-[1.15] md:text-8xl md:leading-[1.15]">
          BORA FAZER
          <br />
          MÚSICA DE VERDADE?
        </h1>
        <p class="balance mx-auto mt-6 max-w-md font-display text-lg leading-snug tracking-wide text-white [text-shadow:0_2px_6px_rgba(0,0,0,0.95),0_4px_16px_rgba(0,0,0,0.7)]">
          Gravação, mixagem e masterização com o Produtor Eder Machado.
        </p>

        <a
          href={WHATSAPP_URL}
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="mt-8 inline-flex items-center gap-2.5 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-purple to-brand-pink px-8 py-4 font-accent text-lg uppercase tracking-wide text-white [text-shadow:none]"
        >
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="h-5 w-5 fill-white"><path d="M12 2a10 10 0 0 0-8.6 15.1L2 22l5.1-1.3A10 10 0 1 0 12 2Zm0 18.2a8.1 8.1 0 0 1-4.2-1.2l-.3-.2-3 .8.8-2.9-.2-.3A8.2 8.2 0 1 1 12 20.2Zm4.5-6.1c-.2-.1-1.4-.7-1.7-.8s-.4-.1-.6.1-.7.8-.9 1-.3.2-.6 0a6.7 6.7 0 0 1-2-1.2 7.4 7.4 0 0 1-1.4-1.7c-.1-.2 0-.4.1-.5s.2-.3.4-.4a1.6 1.6 0 0 0 .2-.4.5.5 0 0 0 0-.4c0-.1-.6-1.5-.8-2s-.4-.4-.6-.4h-.5a1 1 0 0 0-.7.3 2.9 2.9 0 0 0-.9 2.2 5.1 5.1 0 0 0 1.1 2.7 11.6 11.6 0 0 0 4.4 3.9c.6.3 1.1.4 1.5.5a3.6 3.6 0 0 0 1.6.1 2.7 2.7 0 0 0 1.8-1.2 2.1 2.1 0 0 0 .1-1.2c-.1-.1-.2-.2-.5-.3Z"/></svg>
          Falar com o Eder agora
        </a>
        <p class="mt-3 text-xs leading-relaxed tracking-wide text-white/90">Fale direto com o Produtor Eder Machado</p>
        <p class="mt-1 text-xs leading-relaxed tracking-wide text-white/80">
          Loops e instrumentos dele já tocaram em produções da Netflix, do SBT e no hit
          "Zona de Perigo" (Léo Santana)
        </p>

        <div class="mx-auto mt-14 flex justify-center">
          <a href="#proximo" aria-label="Descer para a próxima seção" class="scroll-hint block">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="h-5 w-5 fill-white/70"><path d="M12 16.5 4.5 9l1.4-1.4L12 13.7l6.1-6.1L19.5 9z" /></svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- FORK: os dois mundos -->
    <section id="proximo" class="px-6 pb-4">
